:'''Mitilimem:''' Hehe... you're eating pumpkins, but you know nothing about the wonders it holds, mem.
:'''Mitilimem:''' At first, the pumpkin wears a hard shell. However, once opened, you discover a heart that's soft and tender.
:'''Mitilimem:''' After a slow and gentle simmer, the lines between pumpkin and broth begin to fade. The savory depth of meat and the mellow sweetness of pumpkin intertwine... In that pot, all the world's good and evil, truth and lies, seem to fuse as one...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why is it always you?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You look really familiar.
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504132406-->
:'''Mitilimem:''' Hehe, have I been found out? As expected, someone like me, a true gourmet, can never go unnoticed, mem.
:'''Mitilimem:''' May these culinary insights spark a little inspiration at your table, mem.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
